N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 4 ยง 203.3 - Objections

State Regulations

Any objections to the granting of the application may be
filed and served in the same manner as the application by any person or
employee organization within 15 working days after receipt by the board of the
application; provided, however, that the board may excuse the late filing of
objections because of extraordinary circumstances. Notes
